        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            



<p>Dr Sir.      <date when="1825-07-30">30th July1825</date></p>

<p>I have understood that in consequence of the death of <persName>Mr. Garver</persName>
the league is of Course vacant that was intended for him even if<pb n="1162"/>
the Deed is out there will not be the necessary improvement made
to hold it I have thought proper to apprise you that I am willing
to take that place You will inform me by <persName>Mr. Jamison</persName>. If you
do not grant me this I Have improved the <placeName>seventh league in Bay
Prarara</placeName> and shall rely upon the faith of the <persName>Government </persName>to attain it,</p>

<p><persName>P. Powell</persName></p>
<p>[Addressed :]<persName>Colo S. F. Austin</persName> <placeName>San Filipe de Austin</placeName></p>


        </div1>
